    <h2 style="text-align: center;">📘 Discrete Mathematics 단원 목록</h2>

    <div style="text-align: right; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <a href="/subjects/discretemath/new" style="background: #3498db; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none;">
